headline: Earth Month Challenge: Republic Services Encourages Consumers to Recycle Plastic Water Bottles
summary: Republic Services is challenging consumers this Earth Month to take action and recycle their plastic water bottles. The recycling rate for single-use water bottles is only 33%1, meaning that nearly 7 in 10 bottles never make it into a recycling bin.
